Author: ZerOxCalx
Text: When you're feeling guilty for eating incase of back peddling and gaining, but knowing it's not going to cause you to gain like the 100lb is definitely an awful battle to have going on inside your head.

Author: mangpd
Text: Wow that's literally been me on and off the past couple of weeks. Like some days I'll be fine and stay under 800, and other days I'll eat around 1600-1800 for no reason but I bought something sweet from my dining hall! It's really annoying because it feels bad, but also it's not a binge since I didn't eat all that much compared to other people? So weird :/
